Package: snakeplot
Title: Serpentine Plots for Long Timeline, Sequential and Survey Data
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mohammed", "Saqr", email = "saqr@saqr.me",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
    person("Sonsoles", "Lopez-Pernas",
           role = "aut"))
Description: Visualize long timelines, extended sequences and temporally
    chained survey responses and experience sampling data using intuitive
    serpentine (snake) plots. Supports distribution bars,
    tick-mark plots, inter-item correlation arcs, faceted multi-construct
    panels, and daily time-of-day positioning for ecological momentary
    assessment data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: graphics, grDevices, stats
LazyData: true
